## ğŸš€ Quick Start

1. **Update FormSubmit Email**
   - In `index.html`, line ~1250, replace:
     ```html
     <form id="contactForm" action="https://formsubmit.co/your-email@example.com" method="POST">
     ```
     with your actual email address.

2. **Update Thank You Redirect**
   - In `index.html`, line ~1251, update:
     ```html
     <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://yourdomain.com/thank-you.html">
     ```
     with your actual domain.

3. **Replace Product Images**
   - Current implementation uses inline SVG placeholders for lamps
   - Replace `data:image/svg+xml,...` in product cards with actual lamp images:
     ```html
     <img src="assets/lamps/terra.webp" alt="Terra Lamp" class="lamp-img">
     ```
   - Recommended format: **WebP** or **AVIF** (with JPEG fallback)
   - Recommended dimensions: **800Ã—1200px** (portrait, high quality)

